*Both D1 and D2
-implementation of applying  boundary conditions in the final step for fg scheme: parameter bcStep in constants.py
-wavePacket - initial condition creation
in 1D set functiontype = 'defined' in sound_wave_params.py and define in sound_wave_defined_params.py the function w
in 2D set timesZArgW = 1  in sound_wave_params.py
-periodicType = refl  (used for reflexion) : parameter in sound_wave_params.py
-plot velocity fourier transform graphic plotVelFFT = True in notifier_params.py(2D) and in sound_wave_params.py(1D)

Test3D

plotAnalitical param in notifier_params: set this to True only in the case of homogenous medium , timesZArgW = 1(not impl for wave packet) and wType = "pot" or wType="all" and argType="x" or "y"
the function defined w may be a function such that initial rho, pres and vel = const * w(z). In this case set wType param in sound_wave_params.py to "all"
If w represents the velocity potential set it to "pot"
 
Tests:
Test moving plane in homogenous medium
set in sound_wave_params.py:
mediumType = "homog"
periodicType = "repeat" 
wType = "all"
timesZArgW = 1 
functionType = "sine"
argType = "x", "y", "d1"
set in notifier_params.py:
plotAnalitical=True in the case of argType="x" and "y"

files carton_*.mp4


Test gaussian function in homogenous medium with periodicType="refl"
set in sound_wave_params.py:
mediumType = "homog"
periodicType = "refl"
wType = "all"
timesZArgW = 1
functionType = "gauss"
argType = "r"
set in constants.py:
domainType="centered"
set in notifier_params.py:
plotAnalitical=False

file gauss_rad_refl_color.mp4


Test gaussian function in homogenous medium with periodicType="diff"
set in sound_wave_params.py:
mediumType = "homog"
periodicType = "diff"
wType = "all"
timesZArgW = 1
functionType = "gauss"
argType = "r"
set in constants.py:
domainType="centered"
set in notifier_params.py:
plotAnalitical=False

file gauss_rad_diff_color.mp4

Wave packet 2d in homogeneous medium

set in sound_wave_params.py:
mediumType = "homog"
periodicType = "refl"
wType = "all"
timesZArgW = 2
set in notifier_params.py:
plotAnalitical=False

files wave_packet_2D_hom_refl_*.mp4


Wave packet 2d in inhomogeneous medium
set in sound_wave_params.py:
mediumType = "inhomog"
periodicType = "refl"
wType = "all"
timesZArgW = 2
change ze, we, densFunc(setiings for inhom medium - at the begining of the file) and zc, k0, W (wave packet settings - at the end of the file)

set in notifier_params.py:
plotAnalitical=False

files wave_packet_2D_inhom*_refl_*.mp4


